{"tid":1216524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］今日去完野餐 唔見左銀包","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:05:11.000Z","uid":106093,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"095195a5dedd8327bc0176af8a3e6294ccad215e","tid":1216524,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩唔小心唔見左銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑色皮<br />\n打開個位有印住chi hong既字<br />\n入面有6，700港紙 千幾台幣<br />\n有身份證 一堆相好重要<br />\n有學生證<br />\n但係盡量唔好打返學校<br />\n岩岩幫完學校搞罷課 <br />\n同學校企硬左<br />\n好唔開心 點知戇鳩鳩<br />\n係麥當勞道落山條路<br />\n去到金鐘廊個段路唔見銀包<br />\n岩岩考完DSE先返part time<br />\n真係我成份身家黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果無哂呢啲錢真係幫唔到大家手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家香港人幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Klaus1006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKlaus1006&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=52824dce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Klaus1006</a>"},{"pid":"aabdab3f1156ee708fa49b2e924dffe73d9d42d0","tid":1216524,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb5373097367f523b0d80440fbb96681c28b6529","tid":1216524,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5290d50baa797ad568f096c6ff819b15468e5ec5","tid":1216524,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19897c83907b818bb7d2452ebc828da0df354ff3","tid":1216524,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:18:57.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"8c4c5bbbce8a92635fe0a13ed309b4cc3031b4dd","tid":1216524,"uid":153847,"like":0,